    "title": "Torgue got more BOOM!",
    "description": "Rockets explode on impact for splash damage and drop a child grenade that detonates about 1 second later for splash. The child grenade scales with grenade damage bonuses. Cannot score critical hits; as a non-Jakobs assault rifle it also has reduced critical damage."
  },
  "notes": "Point-blank shots can damage you and allies via the rocket and child grenade. With the Grog Nozzle drunk effect it can fire 6 rockets, each dropping a grenade. Kills count for Pull the Pin. Absorb shields can absorb the main rocket as launcher ammo; the child grenade cannot be absorbed. Amp shields boost both rocket and child grenade. Grenade damage bonuses boost the child grenade. Axton: does not benefit from Steady. Gaige: poor for Anarchy; Close Enough will not bounce rockets, and high Anarchy risks self-hits. Krieg: strong at range with Strip the Flesh, Blood Bath, and Pa",
